hits.shortDescription: The Dinky 18 is part of The Coach Originals, a collection of archival-inspired and vintage bags that celebrates our legacy and authentic New York heritage. Reimagined for today, this minimalist crossbody-to-clutch design was first introduced in 1973. Crafted of quilted nappa leather and finished with our iconic turnlock closure, "the little bag that could" (and did) is a longtime Coach favorite. Some styles are just too good to leave in the archives.

hits.shortDescription: Built for the urban obstacle course, our lightweight Mid Top sneaker is made with proprietary Coach CitySole technology for maximum comfort and flexibility. Based on traditional mid-cut court shoes, this retro-style silhouette sits at the intersection of fashion and function. Crafted in a mix of velvety suede, smooth leather and high-shine metallic leather accented with our Signature, it features shock-absorbing cushioned pods in the heel that provide all-day support. It's finished with a grooved sole for superior movement and traction. Your feet will thank you.
